data.description: 2.37% Assumable Interest Rate!!! Experience the epitome of urban living in this 3 bed / 2.5 bath, brick front-end unit rowhome, ideally situated at 2026 Fountain St in Fell's Point, 21231. Enjoy a captivating rooftop deck with unparalleled waterfront views, offering a serene escape & vibrant entertainment space. Discover a sun-drenched living room with exposed brick, elegant crown molding, and engineered hardwood floors that create a warm, inviting atmosphere. The open-plan layout connects the living area to a sophisticated dining space and a state-of-the-art gourmet kitchen. Culinary dreams come true here with a central island breakfast bar, lustrous granite countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The main level also features a chic powder room for your convenience. Ascend to the upper floors, where natural light bathes two cozy bedrooms, complemented by a full bathroom with a modern shower/tub combination. The third level is dedicated to the luxurious owner's suite, a spacious and airy haven with a sumptuous bath. Indulge in the large soaking tub, a sleek glass-enclosed shower with elegant tile finishes, and a dual vanity, crafting a private spa-like experience. Located just a block from the vibrant Waterfront Promenade, this home is a jewel in Fells Point, offering a perfect blend of tranquility and city excitement. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your own – an unmatched offering in city living.
